articles.description: Trae Young's spirits were buoyed by a surprise phone call Wednesday from Hall of Famer Oscar Robertson, who gave the Sooners freshman "some good advice."
articles.headline: Trae Young gets 'good advice' from Hall of Famer Oscar Robertson

images.name: Oklahoma falls to Texas Tech, suffers fourth consecutive loss

videos.description: Brandon Averette hits from the elbow to put Oklahoma State up 13-6 over the Sooners.
videos.headline: Averette hits jumper to put Cowboys up 7

videos.description: Jamuni McNeace gets a big two-handed block on Brandon Averette for the Sooners.
videos.headline: McNeace rejects Averette at the rim

videos.description: Kendall Smith gets inside on the fast break for the score to put Oklahoma State up 25-6.
videos.headline: Smith puts Cowboys up 19 with driving layup

videos.description: Trae Young pulls up close to the mid-court logo and gets a lucky bounce for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Young gets the bounce on deep 3

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Jeffrey Carroll takes advantage of his team's hustle and hits a 3-pointer which is followed by deep 3 from Trae Young.
videos.headline: Carroll hits 3, Young responds with his own

videos.description: Trae Young turns the ball over with a long pass through traffic and commits a foul on the other end.
videos.headline: Young ends first half with erratic sequence

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Kendall Smith pulls up for a quick-fire 3 with a second left on the clock to put the Cowboys up 42-30 at the half.
videos.headline: Smith hits buzzer-beater 3 to end half

videos.description: Trae Young had 14 points when Oklahoma entered halftime with a 12-point deficit against the Cowboys, and his knee needed some attention as well.
videos.headline: Young struggles in first half for Sooners

videos.description: Trae Young finds Rashard Odomes in the paint for a layup, forcing a timeout as the Sooners cut their deficit to 5.
videos.headline: Young fires to Odomes on the run for bucket

videos.description: Brady Manek throws it down off the long pass from Trae Young to make it a 3-point game.
videos.headline: Manek dunks off Young steal

videos.description: Trae Young gets beyond the arc after the inbounds pass and hits from long range for the Sooners.
videos.headline: Young loses defenders for another deep 3

videos.description: Trae Young breaks ankles with a cutback and knocks down a 3-pointer to cut the Sooners' deficit to 2.
videos.headline: Young makes defender slip and hits 3

videos.description: Trae Young rolls off the screen and hits a 3-pointer to give OU its first lead of the day.
videos.headline: Young accentuates 3 with a shimmy

videos.description: Lindy Waters III throws down after a long possession for the Cowboys.
videos.headline: Waters dunks after hectic sequence

videos.description: Tavarius Shine puts the Cowboys up with a 3-pointer, which is quickly followed by a huge 3 from Trae Young.
videos.headline: Young takes lead back with logo 3

videos.description: Trae Young puts OU up 3 with his eighth 3-pointer of the day.
videos.headline: Young cuts back for another 3

videos.description: Trae Young loses his dribble off his foot and it's picked up by Mitchell Solomon, who finds Tavarius Shine for the jam.
videos.headline: Shine dunks off Young turnover

videos.description: Trae Young heads to the line after a big block and foul from Lindy Waters III late in the game.
videos.headline: Young draws late foul from Waters

videos.description: Kendall Smith hits a tying 3-pointer with 6 seconds left in regulation sending Bedlam to overtime.
videos.headline: Smith hits 3 to send it to OT

videos.description: Khadeem Lattin rejects a shot from Kendall Smith off the backboard in overtime.
videos.headline: Lattin blocks Smith off the glass

videos.description: Trae Young loses the ball in traffic setting up a fastbreak layup for Kendall Smith to put the Cowboys up 4 in OT.
videos.headline: Young turnover leads to fastbreak bucket for OSU

videos.description: Trae Young gets the finger roll after multiple offensive rebounds cutting the lead to 2.
videos.headline: Young scores after multiple chances for OU

videos.description: Trae Young gets double-teamed in the closing seconds of overtime and misses badly as time expires.
videos.headline: OSU fans storm the court after Young's missed shot
OKST VS OKLA

videos.description: Trae Young overcomes a rocky start to score 48 points in Oklahoma's 83-81 overtime loss to Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Young's 48 points not enough to prevent OT loss

videos.description: Trae Young tied a Big 12 record with 48 points against Oklahoma State and he hit 14 shots from the field along the way.
videos.headline: Every Trae Young bucket en route to his 48 points
